description:
Fuyuka Liqueur (formerly known as http://anidb.net/ch25731 [Hazuki Fuyuka]), at the age of about 45 years, during the events of http://anidb.net/a2334 [Silent Mobius: The Motion Picture].
She has magic abilities (not relevant in http://anidb.net/a455 [the TV series] but shown in more depth during http://anidb.net/a2334 [the first movie]).
She died during the flashback part of this first movie which takes place in the year 2024.
name: Fuyuka Liqueur
